videos.headline: Kentucky and Louisville kickoff game with scuffle
videos.description: Louisville' Hassan Hall returns the opening kickoff 20 yards and after the play a Kentucky player takes a tumble and the teams exchange blows.

videos.headline: Snell scores 45th career rushing TD
videos.description: In the wildcat, Benny Snell Jr. takes the snap and turns the corner for a 7-yard touchdown to put Kentucky on the board.

videos.headline: Wilson leaps in for a 3-yard TD
videos.description: Kentucky QB Terry Wilson takes the snap, runs to the outside, cuts back in to cross up a Louisville defender and jumps in for a 3-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Cunningham erupts for a 75-yard TD
videos.description: Malik Cunningham looks to throw but finds opening and bursts for a 75-yard touchdown run to put Louisville on the board.

videos.headline: Snell runs in a 24-yard TD
videos.description: Benny Snell Jr. gets the handoff, breaks a tackle and flies into the end zone for a 24-yard touchdown to give Kentucky a 21-7 lead.

videos.headline: Mbanasor ejected for targeting
videos.description: Louisville's P.J. Mbanasor launches with the crown of his helmet and is ejected for targeting on Kentucky QB Terry Wilson.

videos.headline: Wilson connects with Bowden for a 28-yard TD
videos.description: Kentucky QB Terry Wilson takes the snap, scrambles, launches and hits a wide-open Lynn Bowden Jr. for a 28-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: Wilson find Bowden for a 13-yard TD
videos.description: Terry Wilson stays in the pockets and rips a 13-yard touchdown to Lynn Bowden Jr. to give Kentucky a 35-10 lead before the half.

videos.headline: Crum sounds off on Lorenzo Ward
videos.description: Micky Crum III gets an unsportsmanlike conduct call and gets into an argument with interim coach Lorenzo Ward who takes his helmet, but Crum pleads and gets back in the game.

videos.headline: Ali hauls in 1st career TD
videos.description: Terry Wilson hits Josh Ali for a 32-yard touchdown; Wilson third pass touchdown of the night and Ali's first career touchdown.

videos.headline: Rose turns on the jets for a 75-yard TD
videos.description: Kentucky's Asim Rose bursts through the hole and takes it to the house for a 75-yard touchdown.
